\fs24 \cf0 Project.
\f0\b0  Notably \'97 turns meeting recordings into searchable transcripts + concise, timestamp-cited notes & action items, viewable in a simple web app and exportable.\

\f1\b Team & roles.
\f0\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
