\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Dylan (CEO): backend/API integration, coordination\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Bryce (COO): features/users/timeline, docs/QA\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Rob (CIO): UX direction, architecture guardrails, infra liaison\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 David (Lead Eng): Figma/UI, frontend implementation\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 Current phase.
\f0\b0  Milestone 2 (requirements, UI/UX, ERD, architecture, API docs). M1 is done.\

\f1\b Stack (decided).
\f0\b0  React; FastAPI + Uvicorn; Redis + RQ; MinIO; PostgreSQL; ffmpeg; Whisper API; GPT; Supabase Auth; Docker Compose (Postgres, Redis, MinIO).\

\f1\b MVP scope (semester).
\f0\b0  Upload \uc0\u8594  Transcribe (segments w/ timestamps) \u8594  Summarize (bullets + action items w/ citations) \u8594  Browse/Search \u8594  Export (PDF/email). Caps: \u8804 60 min, \u8804 1 GB. De-scoped for now: real-time capture, advanced analytics/diarization UI, heavy org/permissions, fancy UI polish.\

