\f1\b What\'92s done.
\f0\b0  M1 doc, Figma/storyboards, Tech overview doc, Logo, ERD v2, API Doc (draft); UX tweaks: sidebar, settings (dark mode + language), profile link.\

\f1\b Next actions (vertical slice).
\f0\b0  Freeze schemas for 3 endpoints; create tables & indexes; wire Upload \uc0\u8594  MinIO \u8594  enqueue RQ job (fake worker ok) \u8594  swap in Whisper API \u8594  store Transcript/Segments \u8594  add GPT summary \u8594  SummaryBullets + BulletCitations \u8594  minimal React UI.\

\f1\b Risks & guardrails.
\f0\b0  Audio quality, summary hallucinations, scope creep, long files/costs \uc0\u8594  timestamp citations, caps, background jobs, small eval set.\
