\
## Why\
- Versioned, reviewable schema changes; enables moving from SQLite \uc0\u8594  Postgres smoothly.\
\
## How to test\
1) rm -f dev.db\
2) alembic upgrade head\
3) Start server; run README upload; status becomes `done`; result returns segments+citations.\
\
## Notes\
- Future schema changes should be via `alembic revision --autogenerate` + `upgrade`.\
